  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The following terms are used in this discussion: "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "termList",
          "items": [
            {
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Client"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "The initiator of an SSL session. The canonical example of a client is a web browser communicating with an HTTPS URL."
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Server"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "An entity that accepts requests for SSL sessions made by clients. An example is a secure web server."
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "SSLSession"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "An entity whose existence is bounded by calls to the functions "
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "reference",
                        "isActive": true,
                        "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1400161-sslhandshake"
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": " and "
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "reference",
                        "isActive": true,
                        "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1397869-sslclose"
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": ". An active session is in some state between these two calls, inclusive."
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "term": {
                "inlineContent": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "SSLSessionContext"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "definition": {
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "inlineContent": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "The state associated with one session. A session context cannot be reused for multiple sessions."
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Most applications need only a few of the functions in this API, which are normally called in the following sequence:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Prepare for a session"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "unorderedList",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1393063-sslcreatecontext"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to create a new SSL session context."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Write the "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/sslwritefunc"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " and "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/sslreadfunc"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " I/O functions and register them with Secure Transport by calling the "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1396081-sslsetiofuncs"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " function."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Establish a connection using "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/cfnetwork"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": ", BSD Sockets, or Open Transport. Then call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1398843-sslsetconnection"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to specify the connection to which the SSL session context applies."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1393047-sslsetpeerdomainname"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to specify the fully-qualified domain name of the peer to which you want to connect (optional but highly recommended)."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1392400-sslsetcertificate"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to specify the certificate to be used in authentication (required for server side, optional for client)."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Start a session"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "unorderedList",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1400161-sslhandshake"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to perform the SSL handshake and establish a secure session. "
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Maintain a session"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "unorderedList",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "To transfer data over the secure session, Secure Transport calls your "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1400864-sslwrite"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " and "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1394324-sslread"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " functions as needed."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "End a session"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "unorderedList",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/1397869-sslclose"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to close the secure session."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Close the connection and dispose of the connection reference."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Release the SSL session context by calling "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1521153-cfrelease"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "inlineContent": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "If you called "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "codeVoice",
                              "code": "SSLGetPeerCertificates"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to obtain any certificates, call "
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "reference",
                              "isActive": true,
                              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1521153-cfrelease"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": " to release the certificate reference objects."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In many cases, it is easier to use the CFNetwork API than Secure Transport to implement a simple connection to a secure (HTTPS) URL. See "
            },
            {
              "type": "link",
              "title": "CFNetwork Programming Guide",
              "destination": "https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/Networking/Conceptual/CFNetwork/Introduction/Introduction.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP30001132"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " for documentation of the CFNetwork API and the CFNetworkHTTPDownload sample code for an example of code that downloads data from a URL. If you specify an HTTPS URL, this routine automatically uses Secure Transport to encrypt the data stream."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For functions to manage and evaluate certificates, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/security/certificate_key_and_trust_services"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
